text: Benoit Buratti (born 10 November 1997) is a French freestyle skier. He competed in the 2017 FIS Freestyle World Ski Championships, and represented France at the 2018 Winter Olympics in PyeongChang. ==References== == External links == * * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:French male freestyle skiers Category:Olympic freestyle skiers of France Category:Freestyle skiers at the 2018 Winter Olympics
